School Ties;;68;;60;;PG-13;;When David Greene (Brendan Fraser) receives a football scholarship to a prestigious prep school in the 1950s, he feels pressure to hide the fact that he is Jewish from his classmates and teachers, fearing that they may be anti-Semitic. He quickly becomes the big man on campus thanks to his football skills, but when his Jewish background is discovered, his worst fears are realized and his friends (Matt Damon, Chris O'Donnell) turn on him with violent threats and public ridicule.;;Drama;;Robert Mandel;;1992;;Brendan Fraser,Matt Damon,Chris O'Donnell,Randall Batinkoff,Andrew Lowery,Cole Hauser,Ben Affleck,Anthony Rapp,Amy Locane,Peter Donat,Zeljko Ivanek,Kevin Tighe,Michael Higgins,Ed Lauter;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/school_ties